Blang programming language
==========================

Data types:
===========
The only data type available in blang is integer

Variables:
==========
Variables don't need to be defined.

Booleans:
=========
Expression is condiered to be true if it's value is not equal to 0.

Structure:
==========
program
  {statements}
  return {expression};
endprogram

Statements:
===========
assignment: 
  {id} := {expression};

if statement:
  if {expression} then
    {statements}
  else
    {statements}
  end if;

while statement
  while {expression} do
    {statements}
  end while;

Operators:
==========
Available operators: +, -, *, \, mod.

Example:
========
See testProgram.blang

Cele:
zdefiniować język, zrobić kompilator i interpreter.

Jak zbudowano kompilator, co jest wynikiem.
Jak działa interpreter

Napisać podręcznik użytkownika.
napisać program w edytorze.
Jak uruchomić interpretator